@startuml seq_26_configure_community
title Sequence Diagram: UC-26 Configure Community

actor Moderator
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Community Controller" as Controller
participant "Community Service" as Service
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
participant "Community Repo" as Repo

Moderator -> Frontend: (1.1/2.1/3.1) Update settings & media, then Save
Frontend -> Controller: (3.2) PUT /api/communities/{id}/settings (multipart form)
Controller -> Service: (4.1) Update Community Settings
Service -> Repo: (4.2) Verify ownership or moderator access
Repo --> Service: (4.3) Access confirmed

alt New avatar or banner uploaded
    Service -> Cloudinary: (2.2) Upload new image stream
    Cloudinary --> Service: (2.3) Return Media URLs & IDs
end

Service -> Repo: (5.1) Update Community record in DB
Repo --> Service: (5.2) Record updated
Service --> Controller: (6.1) Saved Settings Data
Controller --> Frontend: (6.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> Moderator: (6.3) Show success message & refresh UI
@enduml
